                    <span>This is a great all around prep book for visiting Basque country.  I then took it with me on my trip.....and everywhere I went in San Sebastian, Bilbao, etc people said: 'Oh, yes.....Kurlansky is far and away the best book about Basque country.'  Any questions?</span>
                  
